13. Bxe5 { Now I am suffering only for one pawn! } Ng4 { That was my desperation. I did not want to resign on move 13 so I continued my suffering for a few moves. Almost anything is winning now. } ( 13...O-O-O { I am 100% sure that Giri would have found the only winning contnuation. } 14.Bxc6! Qxc6 { White's attack is going smoothly. } { 14...bxc6 15.Rb8+!? Kd7 16.Rb7++- The king has to go to the e-file. No comment. } 15.Nb5!? Qa6 16.Qd4+- ) 
